{"tid":1784023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金鐘控訴暴力集會數百人參與","createTime":"2019-12-15T10:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T14:13:13.000Z","uid":25468,"like":23,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"86785c8d7974a8cfbeba7dcec202f1fd14872f37","tid":1784023,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191215/photo/bkn-20191215130009916-1215_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191215140943\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191215130009916-1215_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191215140943&h=21b23122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日(15日)分別有多批網民發起不同的示威及集會活動，其中在添馬公園舉行「控訴暴力大集會」，邀請多名在修例風波中曾被「私了」暴力對待的市民，分享遭遇。<br />\n<br />\n近中午1時，已有逾500人聚集，有人派發支持警察的傳單、和小型五星旗。大部分參與者為中年人士，部分人操流利國語，現場有糾察員維持秩序，部分人更與在場戒備的警員合照及為警員鼓勵打氣。<br />\n<br />\n市民陳先生自稱9月1日前往天水圍西鐵站途中，見有警察被罵，他大叫「支持警察」後被人拳打腳踢。市民黃小姐聲稱曾自發清理路面的垃圾及地磚，即被數個黑衣人以粗口指罵，其中1人更用磚頭打她頭部致她受傷，需到醫院縫5針，冀施暴者受法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191215/bkn-20191215130009916-1215_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191215%2Fbkn-20191215130009916-1215_00822_001.html&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=04bf3fd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191215/bkn-20191215130009916-1215_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/15/51ltUn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2F51ltUn.png&h=b91749f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4faee5cb070ee2bbb0be4d7b7b97c94fa628a14e","tid":1784023,"uid":202524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" da